    ((:with "engineering/COMPOSER-1.1.ENG.slat" :note "TUI is companion to Composer TUI mode — same screen buffer approach could power composer/render-tui updates.")
     (:with "engineering/IDE-WAVE-2-2026-07-19.ENG.slat" :note "TUI mirrors Wave 2 pair-programming + reading-state work.")
     (:with "memory/project_motoi_branding_2026_07_17.md" :note "Branding memo now supersedes the pink/green/brown lock — cherry-tree replaces it, keeping the three-stripe motif shape.")
     (:with "memory/project_motoi_is_the_new_speak_and_spell_2026_07_17.md" :note "The TUI's F-key + Tab focus-cycle interface is the terminal cousin of the Speak-and-Spell button doctrine."))

  :open-questions
